=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex5 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 893 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 892.7977
  harmonic_decay_rate: -1.9219
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8366
  pitch_clarity: 17.3978
  inharmonicity: 0.1859
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -9.1567
  resonance_freq: 968.9941

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 5
// Author: SC Documentation
